{
  "stem": "2133.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there for about three months, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we heard that my two sisters is alive-- Elizabeth and Margaret.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went back to Czechoslovakia-- went back to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a Belgian general who was a political prisoner, and they met after the war with my two sisters in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they send a message to my older sister, who was living in Brussels, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when this general came back, they gave the message to my sister that Elizabeth and Margaret went back to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I heard that, I went to the Czechoslovakian Council.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told them that, you know, I want to go back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I knew my two sisters that they're not very ambitious people, and they would remain there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't want them to remain under the Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The part where we came from, in '43, when Russia took it over, it became [NON-ENGLISH], which means United Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's still under the same occupation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the Czechoslovakian Council advised me not to go back there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if you go back in your age, they pick you up on the street and they take you to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Russians, they-- example, if they needed somebody's store or something, they just went in and they threw all your furniture out and took it over.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had learned that when I got back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I told to the Council, it doesn't matter what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have to go back, because I want to see my sisters, and I don't want them to remain there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't want to live anymore among those people who did this terrible thing to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very difficult, because everything was bombed, bombed out.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
